{"title":"Farewell’s Memory Palace Saddle or Handlebar Pack","link":"https://theradavist.com/farewell-memory-palace-saddle-or-handlebar-pack/","date":1707490140000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1776\" height=\"1184\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/AC2A3551-95C0-4655-85DE-6F455DE4525F-23459-00001693D10BE988.jpg?fit=1200,1184&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/AC2A3551-95C0-4655-85DE-6F455DE4525F-23459-00001693D10BE988.jpg?w=1776&amp;quality=75 1776w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/AC2A3551-95C0-4655-85DE-6F455DE4525F-23459-00001693D10BE988.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/AC2A3551-95C0-4655-85DE-6F455DE4525F-23459-00001693D10BE988.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/AC2A3551-95C0-4655-85DE-6F455DE4525F-23459-00001693D10BE988.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Santa Fe’s own <a href=\"https://www.thisisfarewell.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Farewell Bags</a> is dropping a limited run of its latest bag design, dubbed the Memory Palace. Find out the 411 on this new bag below…<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"1080\" height=\"1079\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-02.jpg.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-02.jpg.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-02.jpg.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-02.jpg.jpg?resize=768,767&amp;quality=75 768w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1079\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-04.jpg.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-04.jpg.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-04.jpg.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-04.jpg.jpg?resize=768,767&amp;quality=75 768w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1079\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-03.jpg.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-03.jpg.jpg?w=1080&amp;quality=75 1080w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-03.jpg.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Farewell_Memory-Palace-03.jpg.jpg?resize=768,767&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p>The Memory Palace is a 16L handlebar or saddle pack, with multiple pockets, a zippered pouch under the main flap and two roomy side pockets. There is a limited release today at 2 PM, MST, with a few color blocked designs available to test interest. Another batch will be on the way shortly.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1776\" height=\"1184\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/E398DED7-C5BB-4CE9-B7DE-2547A1AA09E9-23459-00001693E3757496.jpg?fit=1200,1184&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/E398DED7-C5BB-4CE9-B7DE-2547A1AA09E9-23459-00001693E3757496.jpg?w=1776&amp;quality=75 1776w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/E398DED7-C5BB-4CE9-B7DE-2547A1AA09E9-23459-00001693E3757496.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/E398DED7-C5BB-4CE9-B7DE-2547A1AA09E9-23459-00001693E3757496.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/E398DED7-C5BB-4CE9-B7DE-2547A1AA09E9-23459-00001693E3757496.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1776\" height=\"1184\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/8E13CA93-2B9A-450B-984B-53EB9F5680E3-23459-0000169404E172A2.jpg?fit=1200,1184&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/8E13CA93-2B9A-450B-984B-53EB9F5680E3-23459-0000169404E172A2.jpg?w=1776&amp;quality=75 1776w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/8E13CA93-2B9A-450B-984B-53EB9F5680E3-23459-0000169404E172A2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/8E13CA93-2B9A-450B-984B-53EB9F5680E3-23459-0000169404E172A2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/8E13CA93-2B9A-450B-984B-53EB9F5680E3-23459-0000169404E172A2.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>It attaches to your saddle or handlebars with a Voile Nano strap along a webbing link chain. Head tube spacers are also supplied with an elastic cord to tie the bottom to the head tube.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1776\" height=\"1184\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/93E08B4B-BB3D-45AD-8CA2-9807ACB48270-23459-00001693E91B7F39.jpg?fit=1200,1184&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/93E08B4B-BB3D-45AD-8CA2-9807ACB48270-23459-00001693E91B7F39.jpg?w=1776&amp;quality=75 1776w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/93E08B4B-BB3D-45AD-8CA2-9807ACB48270-23459-00001693E91B7F39.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/93E08B4B-BB3D-45AD-8CA2-9807ACB48270-23459-00001693E91B7F39.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/93E08B4B-BB3D-45AD-8CA2-9807ACB48270-23459-00001693E91B7F39.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1776\" height=\"1184\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/9B81BD90-3B6C-406E-ADFC-9EF6E7B03EE7-23360-0000167EE6F8B780.jpg?fit=1200,1184&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/9B81BD90-3B6C-406E-ADFC-9EF6E7B03EE7-23360-0000167EE6F8B780.jpg?w=1776&amp;quality=75 1776w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/9B81BD90-3B6C-406E-ADFC-9EF6E7B03EE7-23360-0000167EE6F8B780.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/9B81BD90-3B6C-406E-ADFC-9EF6E7B03EE7-23360-0000167EE6F8B780.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/9B81BD90-3B6C-406E-ADFC-9EF6E7B03EE7-23360-0000167EE6F8B780.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Closure is made possible by open ended ladder clips that hook to a link webbing chain on the front of the bag. You can lock these for when the going gets rough or leave them open for quick access.</p>\n<p>Roll over to <a href=\"https://www.thisisfarewell.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Farewell</a> today at 2 PM to see more.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/farewell-memory-palace-saddle-or-handlebar-pack/\">Farewell’s Memory Palace Saddle or Handlebar Pack</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"0e7268f107f3a8b9667be6ec5df4eda8100405fedd5cd7628aca4c36b72d0263","category":"Cycling"}